    {
      "id": "port-ref-walkthrough-step-1",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Step 1",
      "position": {
        "x": -260,
        "y": 40
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 1: Create a Port\n\nCreate a `port` node and set:\n- `target.endpoint` (or `target.ref`)\n- `authority = consume-view`\n- `sourcePayload = node.web.summary`\n\nExpected:\n- [ ] Target resolves\n- [ ] Port renders the consumed view\n- [ ] Edit drawer shows a stable view dropdown"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "port-ref-walkthrough-step-2",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Step 2",
      "position": {
        "x": -260,
        "y": 330
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 2: Switch view payloads\n\nSwitch between `node.web.summary` and `node.web.detail`.\n\nExpected:\n- [ ] Render updates immediately\n- [ ] Dropdown does not lose options\n- [ ] Current selection stays present even if it's legacy/custom"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "port-ref-walkthrough-step-3",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Step 3",
      "position": {
        "x": -260,
        "y": 620
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 3: Preview Mode\n\nCreate a second `port` node pointing at the same target.\n\nSet:\n- `target.mode = preview`\n- `sourcePayload = minimap`\n\nExpected:\n- [ ] Preview/minimap rendering works from only the address\n- [ ] Switching between preview/navigate stays stable"
      }
    },
